**Corps :**
    
    
    {
        "modelId": "model_abc123",
        "name": "my-deployment",
        "region": "us-central1",
        "resources": {
            "cpu": 1,
            "memoryGi": 2,
            "minInstances": 0,
            "maxInstances": 1
        }
